QueryToExecute:
select
  arn as resource,
  engine,
  case
    when enabled_cloudwatch_logs_exports @> '["audit"]' then 'ok'
    else 'alarm'
  end as status,
  case
    when enabled_cloudwatch_logs_exports @> '["audit"]' then title || ' audit logging enabled.'
    else title || ' audit logging disabled.'
  end as reason
  
  , region, account_id
from
  aws_neptune_db_cluster;
